{"tid":1711840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽講有人有山埃中毒症狀 香港藥冊有處方解藥CYANOKIT","createTime":"2019-11-12T12:46:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T05:47:26.000Z","uid":258348,"like":62,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"258234f9b9c1cff63f66b4e47841f346b6456e32","tid":1711840,"uid":258348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T12:46:34.000Z","msg":"tldr: 經醫生確診之後處方Cyanokit；但係因爲係infusion點滴所以要喺醫院/診所做<br />\n<br />\n山埃除咗喺催淚彈高溫react會發出之外<br />\n喺其他燃燒物都會出現<br />\n喺外國山火嘅時候會用到Cyanokit<br />\n香港藥冊有，睇醫生攞處方就可以買；醫院應該會有<br />\n但係佢係Infusion 點滴嚟，所以要喺醫院/診所做15分鐘<br />\n原理係佢裡面有Hydroxocobalamin （維他命b12嘅其中一個form）<br />\n可以pick up 血裡面嘅cyanide react做 Cyanocobalamin （維他命b12嘅另一個form）<br />\n但係一般比b12缺乏症嘅supplement/injection 都只係5mg <br />\nCyanokit係5g，即係1000倍"},{"pid":"1a67f7e05662125c8892caa72fde0344cedbcdf0","tid":1711840,"uid":193999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T12:47:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0cde41c6531125cd5a46894d83d363102c53ae09","tid":1711840,"uid":49300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T12:47:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7956873a87e3e033e90b858c8cc9ead10ea99124","tid":1711840,"uid":250580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T12:47:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a73857753c44948d94360f722a2e419c83b2c404","tid":1711840,"uid":6581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T22:54:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f5c2c5a0dc9c24a539e3f8b8f610702d57302f7a","tid":1711840,"uid":62600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T23:02:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4db2e75c13a6280568ebd86d3e7ba04bbcb3c884","tid":1711840,"uid":160102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T23:04:08.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"b38f3f0245082f980374c3ce7f73944efd2fa4bb","tid":1711840,"uid":3076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T23:41:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"18291260d4da5c3d5a11199c5