.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:57:12.000Z","msg":"如果讀過生物學就知道 能量產生係主要靠線粒體<br />\n而山埃就會令到線粒體內既產生能量步驟受阻<br />\n因為山埃會黏住cytochrome aa2 <br />\n而cyanokit 內既 vitamin B12a 透過注射到身體<br />\nB12a 會更鐘意同cyanide一齊，因此會將cyanide帶走，令佢無辦法佔領住cytochrome aa2 <br />\n最後cyanide同b12a 合成為 我地常見既補健品cyanocolabamin （b12) 直接透過尿排出"},{"pid":"5d986e0bd8ab2d05dbb66f6bda76ec98fa795df8","tid":1711840,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:01:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31d7e4ec2d0c5121369191beb516fc07456ccb42","tid":1711840,"uid":47080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:01:50.000Z","msg":"推俾藥劑師手足睇"},{"pid":"453d5f6ca333279b8ae1768a61acff0192e1687b","tid":1711840,"uid":273188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:01:55.000Z","msg":"點解今日教育局都死唔肯停課，但八大就停課，係咪好鬼呢。<br />\n昨天首次停曬八大，之後就暴力清場，好明顯政府認為滅左你大學生，事件就會完，<br />\n所有其它大學要作最壞打算，準備可以立即徹離，唔可以比人圍困<br />\n對無人性的林鄭來說，唔好誤以為停課係為你地安全着想，佢係想暴力清場。<br />\n仲有，有消息內地生徹走，好明顯為屠殺鋪路<br />\n必須推上國際，要話比世界聽&ldquo;天安門事件&rdquo;又即將發生，仲要係警察想走入八大，消滅整個世代的大學生。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1712238\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1712238</a>"},{"pid":"f556932bc0de7fd33394c00844b1d02ffabd8f16","tid":1711840,"uid":310217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:02:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9e3736ec6e19566f30e46f55369755a421516f8f","tid":1711840,"uid":31561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:05:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"761696ffbbdf5d39e9097af753763e2dbf77e541","tid":1711840,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:07:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ang